elements.expression:
shape "square" fill="#0f1f5e" border="rgba(255,255,255,0)" borderWidth=0 maintainAspect=false
| render

shape "square" fill="#c72a30" border="rgba(255,255,255,0)" borderWidth=0 maintainAspect=false
| render

filters
| essql 
  query="SELECT COUNT(*) total, MONTH(DateofSale) month
FROM \"iowa-liquor\"
GROUP BY month
ORDER BY month"
| pointseries x="total" y="month"
| plot defaultStyle={seriesStyle bars=0.75 horizontalBars=true color="#FFFFFF"} legend=false xaxis=false yaxis=false
| render

shape "circle" fill="#FFFFFF" border="rgba(255,255,255,0)" borderWidth=0 maintainAspect=true
| render

filters
| essql 
  query="SELECT SUM(StateBottleRetail) as retail, SUM(StateBottleCost) as cost, CategoryName.keyword
FROM \"iowa-liquor\"
GROUP BY CategoryName.keyword"
| math "(sum(retail)-sum(cost))/sum(retail)"
| revealImage origin="bottom" image={asset "asset-4fde4c25-adad-4651-8d7b-cd0d8c78a34c"} emptyImage={asset "asset-4f4ee782-59cd-46a8-8c79-24558721f2e0"}
| render

essql query="SELECT CategoryName.keyword
FROM \"iowa-liquor\""
| dropdownControl valueColumn="CategoryName.keyword" filterColumn="CategoryName.keyword"
| render

filters
| essql query="SELECT SUM(VolumeSoldGallons) total
FROM \"iowa-liquor\""
| math "total"
| formatNumber "0.00a"
| metric "Total Gallons" 
  metricFont={font size=48 family="'Open Sans', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif" color="#000000" align="center" lHeight=48} 
  labelFont={font size=14 family="'Open Sans', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif" color="#000000" align="center"}
| render

filters
| essql query="SELECT SUM(SaleDollars) total
FROM \"iowa-liquor\""
| math "total"
| formatNumber "0.00a"
| metric "Total Sales" 
  metricFont={font size=48 family="'Open Sans', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif" color="#000000" align="center" lHeight=48} 
  labelFont={font size=14 family="'Open Sans', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif" color="#000000" align="center"}
| render
